{"tid":2093733,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"人大左先識欣賞學生妹","createTime":"2020-07-04T05:10:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-04T11:04:54.000Z","uid":198624,"like":35,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"992744ef21770ee7cb73c06506c4913213eddde4","tid":2093733,"uid":198624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T05:10:55.000Z","msg":"讀中學果陣鍾意左個女同學<br />\n但係畢業之前最尾都係冇同佢表白，然後上左大學之後就冇乜聯絡<br />\n近排見佢喺ig post嘅相，見佢染左髮又有化妝靚左，係幾正嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但係我發覺望住幅相冇左以前心動嘅感覺<br />\n諗下諗下先發覺我鍾意嘅係佢以前嘅清澀<br />\n我諗呢個亦都係啲人成日話溝學生妹嘅原因<br />\n上到大學的確係有好多靚女，佢地好識打扮，但係同中學果陣嘅女同學硬係有啲分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人大左環境複雜左，呢種情感可能都只係想搵返當日校園生活嘅青春同純真，喺現實世界搵個避風港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ad362720172700c5db44f7f9b54cdc548ed0632","tid":2093733,"uid":132898,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T05:12:45.000Z","msg":"我都人大左先識欣賞伯母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dd72b98c4bce8630beb496c7e2761240cda03d0","tid":2093733,"uid":295672,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T05:12:50.000Z","msg":"以前既學生妹，而家幾多學生妹出黎做PTGF賣相雞，重邊有純情天真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc676295f3231869c66c0034708cca9b931652d4","tid":2093733,"uid":127929,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T05:15:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/itAzQFc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FitAzQFc.jpg&h=1f0913e8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e43dc1ed5513cce7728346944846467431e46959","tid":2093733,"uid":307927,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T05:16:35.000Z","msg":"搵老婆一定搵pure女女啦"},{"pid":"7a745e49e7c89c81e258f3799f905e934f0f57a5","tid":2093733,"uid":198624,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fc676295f3231869c66c0034708cca9b931652d4"